00:04:22.590 --> 00:04:26.780
by giving them quality education
and inculcating in them

00:04:26.780 --> 00:04:28.900
high moral values.

00:04:28.900 --> 00:04:30.670
VINAYAK LOHANI: One
day it struck me

00:04:30.670 --> 00:04:36.900
that I should start a shelter
home for children, children

00:04:36.900 --> 00:04:40.920
from very difficult
backgrounds, and to whom

00:04:40.920 --> 00:04:42.940
I could dedicate my whole life.

00:04:42.940 --> 00:04:48.520
I could bring them up as my own
younger brothers and younger

00:04:48.520 --> 00:04:49.090
sisters.

00:04:49.090 --> 00:04:51.980
So in that spirit, as
a guardian to them,

00:04:51.980 --> 00:04:54.770
I can live my whole life.

00:04:54.770 --> 00:04:58.770
When I decided to
start the shelter home,

00:04:58.770 --> 00:05:04.960
I was first looking for land
where I could start and then do

00:05:04.960 --> 00:05:06.790
some construction in that land.

00:05:06.790 --> 00:05:09.520
But even a small
piece of land was

00:05:09.520 --> 00:05:14.990
costing so much that it was just
beyond any kind of imagination

00:05:14.990 --> 00:05:15.610
that I had.

00:05:15.610 --> 00:05:20.390
So I decided to start
in a rented building.

00:05:20.390 --> 00:05:25.250
I therefore saw a few
buildings and finally zeroed

00:05:25.250 --> 00:05:30.390
on a rented building,
which was nearby

00:05:30.390 --> 00:05:35.340
on campus and rent of which
was around 12,000 rupees.

00:05:35.340 --> 00:05:39.700
So I started taking lectures
for [? NBS ?] parents

00:05:39.700 --> 00:05:41.660
and some coaching and
students in Kolkata.

00:05:41.660 --> 00:05:46.500
And through that, I
could meet this rent.

00:05:46.500 --> 00:05:48.660
NARRATOR: The financial
position of Parivaar

00:05:48.660 --> 00:05:51.320
started improving as
it gained popularity

00:05:51.320 --> 00:05:54.660
within his family,
friends, and colleagues.

00:05:54.660 --> 00:05:58.100
His mother, an ardent believer
in the goodness of people,

00:05:58.100 --> 00:06:00.990
was the first donor of Parivaar.

00:06:00.990 --> 00:06:03.450
Within a year, Vinayak
had enough funds

00:06:03.450 --> 00:06:08.452
to buy two acres of land at 24
Parganas and to start Parivaar.

00:06:08.452 --> 00:06:10.160
VINAYAK LOHANI: So in
this way I started.

00:06:10.160 --> 00:06:12.327
The first three
children I brought

00:06:12.327 --> 00:06:16.000
from a village
around 20 kilometers

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:21.280
from Kolkata from extremely
deprived backgrounds.

00:06:21.280 --> 00:06:28.250
And with that, after 15 days,
another 10 children came.

00:06:28.250 --> 00:06:31.070
So at the end of
say, two months,

00:06:31.070 --> 00:06:33.380
I had around 30
children already.

00:06:33.380 --> 00:06:38.340
I then began to write
email appeals-- first

00:06:38.340 --> 00:06:40.990
to IIM, Kolkata [INAUDIBLE]
because [INAUDIBLE] I

00:06:40.990 --> 00:06:43.222
had access to.

00:06:43.222 --> 00:06:45.180
Though I had written to
more than 1,000 people,

00:06:45.180 --> 00:06:49.430
percentage-wise a very
small percentage responded.

00:06:49.430 --> 00:06:52.470
But still, number-wise it
was around 20, 25 people who

00:06:52.470 --> 00:06:55.844
responded, which was
very encouraging to me

00:06:55.844 --> 00:07:00.010
because I realized that when I'm
just starting this work, even

00:07:00.010 --> 00:07:02.706
at this stage there are people
who are showing confidence

00:07:02.706 --> 00:07:04.540
in me, showing trust in me.

00:07:04.540 --> 00:07:06.470
NARRATOR: As the number
of children grew,

00:07:06.470 --> 00:07:10.590
Vinayak realized that Parivaar
should have its own school

00:07:10.590 --> 00:07:13.830
to cater to the unique need
of and ideal development

00:07:13.830 --> 00:07:16.555
of the children at Parivaar.

00:07:16.555 --> 00:07:20.470
Amar Bharat Vidyapeeth is
affiliated to the West Bengal

00:07:20.470 --> 00:07:22.880
Board of Education
and runs classes

00:07:22.880 --> 00:07:25.110
till the high-school level.

00:07:25.110 --> 00:07:28.400
This ensures that the children
have a recognized certificate

00:07:28.400 --> 00:07:33.800
to continue higher education on
the way to their career paths.

00:07:33.800 --> 00:07:35.590
The Vidyapeeth
teaches the children

00:07:35.590 --> 00:07:39.440
to be proficient in three
languages-- Bengali, English,

00:07:39.440 --> 00:07:40.136
and Hindi.

00:07:40.136 --> 00:07:41.594
VINAYAK LOHANI: So
all our children

00:07:41.594 --> 00:07:43.430
till grade 10 studied here.

00:07:43.430 --> 00:07:47.590
And in grade 11, 12, and for
graduation-- in colleges--

00:07:47.590 --> 00:07:50.700
They attend some
outside institutions,

00:07:50.700 --> 00:07:54.790
which have the stream
they want to study.

00:07:54.790 --> 00:07:56.220
NARRATOR: Every
child at Parivaar

00:07:56.220 --> 00:07:58.800
is able to aspire
for a brighter future

00:07:58.800 --> 00:08:02.460
based on the quality education
and life skills they receive

00:08:02.460 --> 00:08:04.200
at Parivaar.

00:08:04.200 --> 00:08:08.710
The initial focus on children
from urban and rural areas

00:08:08.710 --> 00:08:12.250
was expanded to include
children of highly impoverished

00:08:12.250 --> 00:08:16.460
tribal areas, where even two
square meals were not available

00:08:16.460 --> 00:08:18.962
and malnutrition was rampant.

00:08:18.962 --> 00:08:20.420
