00:08:38.621 --> 00:08:40.120
VINAYAK LOHANI: At
Parivaar, we have

00:08:40.120 --> 00:08:43.000
residential children
from around 14,

00:08:43.000 --> 00:08:48.724
15 different districts, around
12 districts in West Bengal,

00:08:48.724 --> 00:08:53.131
two districts in Jharkhand,
and a few pockets in Bihar

00:08:53.131 --> 00:08:55.880
and Chhattisgarh also.

00:08:55.880 --> 00:08:59.580
NARRATOR: Every year, Parivaar
screens more than 1,500 cases

00:08:59.580 --> 00:09:03.440
of needy children for admission.

00:09:03.440 --> 00:09:07.040
These children are in
the age group of 5 to 10.

00:09:07.040 --> 00:09:09.920
Parivaar has a detailed
pre-admission screening

00:09:09.920 --> 00:09:12.300
process, which
includes a site visit

00:09:12.300 --> 00:09:15.600
to determine that the child is
extremely needy and vulnerable

00:09:15.600 --> 00:09:18.540
and in need of long-term
residential support.

00:09:18.540 --> 00:09:21.370
One of the criteria
in selecting the child

00:09:21.370 --> 00:09:24.300
is to determine that there
is a minimal possibility

00:09:24.300 --> 00:09:27.962
of a dropout of the
child from Parivaar.

00:09:27.962 --> 00:09:29.670
VINAYAK LOHANI: We
ensure that we are not

00:09:29.670 --> 00:09:34.450
looking for a short-term
stay at Parivaar--

00:09:34.450 --> 00:09:37.800
just for, say, a
couple of years or so--

00:09:37.800 --> 00:09:40.820
but for a long-term
transformation.

00:09:40.820 --> 00:09:44.440
So if a child is admitted
at the age of five,

00:09:44.440 --> 00:09:46.580
our aim is start their
higher education, which

00:09:46.580 --> 00:09:50.310
could be graduation and
after that, a job placement.

00:09:50.310 --> 00:09:53.242
Until that level, the
child will be at Parivaar.

00:09:53.242 --> 00:09:55.990
NARRATOR: Most NGO and
government-run shelters

00:09:55.990 --> 00:09:59.800
support the children until
they attain the age of 18.

00:09:59.800 --> 00:10:02.880
The support is withdrawn
after the child turns 18.

00:10:02.880 --> 00:10:05.860
Parivaar has no such age limit.

00:10:05.860 --> 00:10:08.870
VINAYAK LOHANI: I think that
just like in a family how

00:10:08.870 --> 00:10:14.992
a family supports a child to
the last possible conclusion,

00:10:14.992 --> 00:10:16.200
it could be higher education.

00:10:16.200 --> 00:10:18.130
It could be job
placement, depending

00:10:18.130 --> 00:10:20.720
on the potential of
that child, giving

00:10:20.720 --> 00:10:23.200
all kinds of
opportunities to make

00:10:23.200 --> 00:10:24.990
the most of their potential.

00:10:24.990 --> 00:10:31.044
So this was my vision,
that just like a family,

00:10:31.044 --> 00:10:35.920
Parivaar will also hand-hold the
child until the last conclusive

00:10:35.920 --> 00:10:42.320
stage, which does full justice
to his or her potential.

00:10:42.320 --> 00:10:45.470
NARRATOR: Parivaar is now
West Bengal's largest free

00:10:45.470 --> 00:10:49.290
residential institution,
a home to more than 1,000

00:10:49.290 --> 00:10:52.080
less-privileged children
served by a team of deeply

00:10:52.080 --> 00:10:58.150
committed, 170-plus
full-time staff.

00:10:58.150 --> 00:11:00.250
Parivaar has two
campuses furnished

00:11:00.250 --> 00:11:03.200
with dorm-like
housing, a school which

00:11:03.200 --> 00:11:08.010
has its own library,
computer lab, dining

00:11:08.010 --> 00:11:15.820
halls, medical rooms, recreation
halls, playfields, etc.

00:11:25.540 --> 00:11:28.390
Here, every child is
seen as a project.

00:11:28.390 --> 00:11:30.880
And there is a high
degree of adherence

00:11:30.880 --> 00:11:35.240
to an individualized plan
of action for each child.

00:11:35.240 --> 00:11:37.310
Most children, when
admitted into Parivaar,

00:11:37.310 --> 00:11:42.050
are without any exposure
to letters on numerals.

00:11:42.050 --> 00:11:44.920
Parivaar has devised a
structured bridging program

00:11:44.920 --> 00:11:47.920
for children between
the ages of 5 and 10,

00:11:47.920 --> 00:11:50.150
whereby these
children are provided

00:11:50.150 --> 00:11:53.980
tutoring for 6 to 12 months to
bring their education levels

00:11:53.980 --> 00:11:55.717
at par with their age group.

00:11:55.717 --> 00:11:57.633
VINAYAK LOHANI: I think
this is very important

00:11:57.633 --> 00:12:01.450
because this correction has to
be done in the initial phase

00:12:01.450 --> 00:12:01.950
itself.

00:12:01.950 --> 00:12:05.870
At the age of 15, nobody would
want to sit in grade six.

00:12:05.870 --> 00:12:09.843
So the backlog has to be
minimized at the starting point

00:12:09.843 --> 00:12:13.760
itself so that when
they are 10 or 11

00:12:13.760 --> 00:12:17.000
they are actually in
grades 4, or 5, or 6.

00:12:17.000 --> 00:12:18.820
After the bridging,
the children are

00:12:18.820 --> 00:12:23.160
admitted into our own in-campus
school Amar Bharat Vidyapeeth.

00:12:23.160 --> 00:12:25.360
NARRATOR: After school
hours, special tutors

00:12:25.360 --> 00:12:29.960
help the children in enhancing
their academic performances.

00:12:29.960 --> 00:12:33.050
Children who had no
opportunity of going to school,

00:12:33.050 --> 00:12:35.890
whose nutrition,
safety, and well-being

00:12:35.890 --> 00:12:40.010
were also under question, now
start aspiring to be teachers,

00:12:40.010 --> 00:12:43.590
to be engineers, to be
doctors, and to enter

00:12:43.590 --> 00:12:45.961
many such other careers.

00:12:45.961 --> 00:12:49.590
A high happiness quotient
maintained in the family

00:12:49.590 --> 00:12:54.600
is the reason for the negligible
dropout rate at Parivaar.

00:12:54.600 --> 00:12:58.510
The atmosphere around Parivaar
lends itself to self esteem

00:12:58.510 --> 00:13:03.006
and creates hope amongst
the resident children.

00:13:03.006 --> 00:13:07.010
100% of the children of Parivaar
appearing for the board exam

00:13:07.010 --> 00:13:09.320
clear the exam
with decent scores.

00:13:09.320 --> 00:13:13.490
VINAYAK LOHANI: The emotional
and psychological nurturing

00:13:13.490 --> 00:13:16.860
of each child, I think that
that is of a very high level.

00:13:16.860 --> 00:13:20.770
And that, I believe, is the
most important achievement

00:13:20.770 --> 00:13:22.730
of Parivaar.

00:13:22.730 --> 00:13:25.020
Now, second is that
the aspiration level

00:13:25.020 --> 00:13:28.153
of the children completely
changes, because their esteem

00:13:28.153 --> 00:13:31.170
need here is really fulfilled.

00:13:31.170 --> 00:13:36.080
The self-respect and the respect
from others that they get here

00:13:36.080 --> 00:13:38.930
from our Seva
Bharatis, just like

00:13:38.930 --> 00:13:43.070
in a family, how you are
sensitively dealt with.

00:13:43.070 --> 00:13:45.830
NARRATOR: A full-time
staff member of Parivaar

00:13:45.830 --> 00:13:49.110
is fondly referred
to as a Seva Bharati,

00:13:49.110 --> 00:13:52.560
meaning the one who is
devoted to an ideal service.

00:13:52.560 --> 00:13:56.490
The Seva Bharatis cater to all
the needs of the boys as well

00:13:56.490 --> 00:13:57.280
as the girls.

00:13:57.280 --> 00:13:58.705
