00:14:26.095 --> 00:14:28.470
NARRATOR: The children from
the early batches of Parivaar

00:14:28.470 --> 00:14:31.190
are now getting ready to
plunge into the competitive

00:14:31.190 --> 00:14:32.670
professional world.

00:14:32.670 --> 00:14:36.130
Some are working as interns in
industry and corporate offices,

00:14:36.130 --> 00:14:38.660
while others are
strengthening their resumes

00:14:38.660 --> 00:14:41.950
by gaining work experience.

00:14:41.950 --> 00:14:45.280
Parivaar goes beyond
providing good education.

00:14:45.280 --> 00:14:48.140
It also guides the children
in their choice of a career.

00:14:48.140 --> 00:14:49.990
They are set on a
path on which they

00:14:49.990 --> 00:14:52.510
would be able to create
a niche for themselves,

00:14:52.510 --> 00:14:56.000
one conforming to the values
instilled during their stay

00:14:56.000 --> 00:14:56.807
at Parivaar.

00:14:56.807 --> 00:14:57.932
