a potential that needs

00:15:14.250 --> 00:15:16.010
an opportunity for development.

00:15:16.010 --> 00:15:19.530
If they are provided the
right kind of opportunity

00:15:19.530 --> 00:15:21.810
and the right kind
of nurturing, they

00:15:21.810 --> 00:15:24.247
have a tremendous
potential to do well.

00:15:24.247 --> 00:15:25.580
