residential institution

00:16:14.490 --> 00:16:16.060
in the state of West Bengal.

00:16:16.060 --> 00:16:19.960
Vinayak is actively working on
expanding the current Parivaar

00:16:19.960 --> 00:16:23.030
facility from accommodating
1,000 children

