NARRATOR: Inspired by the
teachings of selfless service

00:16:48.685 --> 00:16:51.710
by Sri Rama Krishna,
Swami Vivekananda,

00:16:51.710 --> 00:16:55.240
Vinayak Lohani is
helping transform

00:16:55.240 --> 00:16:57.970
the lives of hundreds
of destitute children,

00:16:57.970 --> 00:17:03.220
not only of West Bengal, but
also those from the surrounding

00:17:03.220 --> 00:17:07.024
states like Jharkhand,
Bihar, and Chhattisgarh.

00:17:09.640 --> 00:17:15.000
Parivaar, his vision, is
now a dream fulfilled.

00:17:15.000 --> 00:17:19.319
This tireless journey of
determination and dedication

00:17:19.319 --> 00:17:22.771
would provide a
role model for many.

