buildup for scaling

00:42:11.470 --> 00:42:14.660
up, for creating the residential
work, and all infrastructure

00:42:14.660 --> 00:42:16.310
facility for the kids.

00:42:16.310 --> 00:42:20.720
So nearly $1.5 million
we raise, and primarily,

00:42:20.720 --> 00:42:23.160
as I said, through individuals.

