moral science kind of classroom

00:45:26.620 --> 00:45:27.270
kind of thing.

00:45:27.270 --> 00:45:30.430
I always think that--
Swami Vivekananda once

00:45:30.430 --> 00:45:33.290
said that if you want
to ever teach anyone

00:45:33.290 --> 00:45:35.860
to be good, if you want
to reform John Doe,

00:45:35.860 --> 00:45:37.750
live with John Doe.

00:45:37.750 --> 00:45:41.510
And if you have any of the
fire of purity, he'll catch it.

00:45:41.510 --> 00:45:43.100
So it's like this.

00:45:43.100 --> 00:45:47.780
It's about living with-- living
and through your own life.

00:45:47.780 --> 00:45:52.010
I think children are quick
learners of how elders

00:45:52.010 --> 00:45:55.330
are behaving, etc cetera,
however so you may philosophize

00:45:55.330 --> 00:45:57.560
