00:47:21.470 --> 00:47:25.290
So it's like one has to
engage, first come and touch,

00:47:25.290 --> 00:47:27.310
and that needs some
kind of an effort.

00:47:27.310 --> 00:47:30.460
You have to get out of your
comfort zone for doing that.

