doing a lot there.

00:51:58.790 --> 00:52:01.440
So many situations
are there when caring.

00:52:01.440 --> 00:52:04.320
So I think you should
have an engagement

00:52:04.320 --> 00:52:06.850
with the whole ecosystem
of organizations,

00:52:06.850 --> 00:52:11.130
in fact, all the
